 best, LEGO game ever created.</div><!----></div><!--[--><div class="review-footer review-footer--critic game-review-footer" data-v-ab61ed06 data-v-c8c74794 data-v-d4a3ca9a><!--[--><a class="game-review-footer__platform" href="/game/lego-batman-legacy-of-the-dark-knight/critic-reviews/?platform=playstation-5" rel="follow" target="_self" data-v-c8c74794><!--[-->PlayStation 5<!--]--></a><!--]--><!--[--><a href="https://adria.ign.com/lego-batman-legacy-of-the-dark-knight/51944/lego-batman-legacy-of-the-dark-knight-recenzija" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><!--[--><span class="review-action-button review-link" data-v-d4a3ca9a data-v-62fd11bd data-v-5fd1ab98><!--[--><!--]--> FULL REVIEW <!--[--><svg class="review-link__icon" data-v-62fd11bd><title>open-full-review</title><use href="#externalLink"></use></svg><!--]--></span><!--]--></a><!--]--><!----><!--[--><!--]--></div><!--]--></div><!--[--><!--]--><!--]--><!--[--><div class="review-card" data-testid="review-card" data-v-95b80213><div class="review-card__content" data-v-95b80213><div class="review-card__date" data-v-95b80213>May 18, 2026</div><a class="review-card__header" href="/publication/vandal/" rel="follow" target="_self" data-v-95b80213><!--[--><div class="c-siteReviewScore_background c-siteReviewScore_background-critic_medium" data-v-95b80213><div class="c-siteReviewScore c-siteReviewScore_green c-siteReviewScore_medium c-siteReviewScore_square c-siteReviewScore_responsiveMobile bg-[#00ce7a] text-[#262626] size-16 text-[2rem] leading-6 rounded-[0.375rem] max-md:size-10 max-md:text-base max-md:leading-6 max-md:rounded-[0.25rem] flex flex-col items-center justify-center font-bold" title="Metascore 85 out of 100" aria-label="Metascore 85 out of 100"><span>85</span></div></div> Vandal<!--]--></a><div class="review-card__quote" data-v-95b80213>LEGO Batman: The Dark Knight&#39;s Legacy clearly stands out as a game crafted with immense affection and respect for the DC Comics license. Its open-world recreati