"slug":2309,"date":2310,"url":1288,"isVideo":1288,"description":2311,"tags":2312,"author":2314,"image":2315},"24c281df-bbb7-45af-86ed-91c736b25c8a","The Worst Video Games of 2024","worst-video-games-of-2024","2024-12-17 22:11:00","Here are Metacritic's lowest-scoring video games released in 2024.",[2313],{"id":1780,"name":1781,"slug":1782},{"byline":1784,"firstName":1785,"id":1786,"lastName":1787,"username":1788},{"id":2316,"filename":2317,"dateCreated":2318,"alt":1288,"credits":1288,"path":2320,"cropGravity":1288,"crop":1288,"caption":2321,"typeName":1288,"imageUrl":1288,"width":1816,"height":1817,"sType":1288,"bucketType":1288,"bucketPath":1288,"mediaType":1288},"4aeb66a3-ae54-4b34-a0bf-f5b3b766b3a1","mainworstgamesof2024.jpg",{"date":2319,"timezone":1794},"2024-12-17 22:12:59.000000","https://www.metacritic.com/a/img/2024/12/17/4aeb66a3-ae54-4b34-a0bf-f5b3b766b3a1/mainworstgamesof2024.jpg","\u003Cp>On this page we rank the  lowest-scoring games released for any  platform between January 1, 2024 and December 31, 2024 in North America.  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>Because we require 4  reviews from professional critics to calculate  a Metascore, any titles with fewer than 4 reviews  are excluded. (For  our \u003Cstrong>best\u003C/strong> lists, we have a higher cutoff, but we think  relaxing the requirements here makes for a more fun worst list. We also  opened the list up to mobile and VR releases, DLC, and compilations.)  And if a single title would have landed on the list multiple times due  to low scores on more than one platform, we only included the  lowest-scoring version.\u003C/p>",{"id":2323,"type":1773,"title":2324,"slug":2325,"date":2326,"url":1288,"isVideo":1288,"description":2327,"tags":2328,"author":2330,"image":2331},"10a3857b-59dd-4fb3-9f5f-c5cde090ae54","Best of 2024: Game of the Year Awards Tracker","2024-game-of-the-year-awards-tracker","2024-11-19 22:38:00","Here are the games released during 2024 that have won major industry awards or received nominations for those awards. We'll update our awards tracker whenever new awards and nominations are announced.",[2329],{"id":1780,"name":1781,"slug":1782},{"byline":1784,"firstName":1785,"id":1786,"lastName":1787,"username":1788},{"id":2332,"filename":2333,"dateCreated":2334,"alt":1288,"credits":1797,"path":2336,"cropGravity":1288,"crop":1288,"caption":1797,"typeName":1288,"imageUrl":1288,"width":1816,"height":1817,"sType":1288,"bucketType":1288,"bucketPath":1288,"mediaType":1288},"aa13a3d7-4cf9-4fe4-a2ef-796b6664b8a4","gameawardstracker2024.jpg",{"date":2335,"timezone":1794},"2024-11-19 22:37:56.000000","https://www.metacritic.com/a/img/2024/11/19/aa13a3d7-4cf9-4fe4-a2ef-796b6664b8a4/gameawardstracker2024.jpg",{"id":2338,"type":1773,"title":2339,"slug":2340,"date":2341,"url":1288,"isVideo":1288,"description":2342,"tags":2343,"author":2345,"image":2346},"95a8f317-a762-4a67-8160-42424634b62d","Hardware Review: PlayStation 5 Pro","playstation-5-pro-console-review-roundup","2024-11-06 17:41:00","Sony's newest version of the PlayStation 5 console is a \"Pro\" model that promises greatly improved visuals thanks to hardware and software enhancements. But do the improvements justify its nearly $700 cost? Find out what critics are saying about the PS5 Pro.",[2344],{"id":1780,"name":1781,"slug":1782},{"byline":1784,"firstName":1785,"id":1786,"lastName":1787,"username":1788},{"id":2347,"filename":2348,"dateCreated":2349,"alt":1288,"credits":2351,"path":2352,"cropGravity":1288,"crop":1288,"caption":1797,"typeName":1288,"imageUrl":1288,"width":1816,"height":1817,"sType":1288,"bucketType":1288,"bucketPath":1288,"mediaType":1288},"23f5ad73-0023-45c4-a756-fd1a3f6adf22","playstation5proconsole.jpg",{"date":2350,"timezone":1794},"2024-11-01 23:26:34.000000","Sony Interactive Entertainment","https://www.metacritic.com/a/img/2024/11/01/23f5ad73-0023-45c4-a756-fd1a3f6adf22/playstation5proconsole.jpg",{"id":2354,"type":1820,"title":2355,"slug":2356,"date":2357,"url":1288,"isVideo":1288,"description":2358,"tags":2359,"author":2361,"image":2366},"adb809c3-4019-4664-9569-4e8c80a6151c","The 20 Best Original Games of the 21st Century","best-original-games-of-the-21st-century","2024-11-05 22:27:00","We rank the highest-scoring \"original\" games (that aren't sequels or remakes or based on existing IP) released since January 1, 2000.",[2360],{"id":1780,"name":1781,"slug":1782},{"byline":1288,"firstName":2362,"id":2363,"lastName":2364,"username":2365},"Nick","7974d639-0d7a-4f9d-bc19-92d8e0ac3199","Hyman","nickhyman",{"id":2367,"filename":2368,"dateCreated":2369,"alt":1288,"credits":2371,"path":2372,"cropGravity":1288,"crop":1288,"caption":2373,"typeName":1288,"imageUrl":1288,"width":1816,"height":1817,"sType":1288,"bucketType":1288,"bucketPath":1288,"mediaType":1288},"316e1b05-16c9-4054-a80c-f04b548e019a","mainbestoriginalgames.jpg",{"date":2370,"timezone":1794},"2024-11-05 22:28:28.000000","FromSoftware/Bandai Namco/Metacritic","https://www.metacritic.com/a/img/2024/11/05/316e1b05-16c9-4054-a80c-f04b548e019a/mainbestoriginalgames.jpg","\u003Cp>\u003Cem>They aren't sequels. They aren't spinoffs. They aren't remakes.  They aren't based on any pre-existing IP. Yes, it's true: The video game  industry sometimes produces completely original games. Below, we reveal  the very best of these original games released since January 1, 2000 as  ranked by their Metascores, a number from 0 to 100 that represents the  overall views of top professional game critics. (The higher the number,  the better the reviews.) \u003C/em>\u003C/p>\u003Cp>\u003Cem>Note that if a title was released on multiple platforms at  roughly the same time, only the version receiving the highest quantity  of reviews was eligible for inclusion. And if a game was later ported to  one or more additional consoles, only the first release was eligible.\u003C/em>\u003C/p>",{"id":2375,"type":1820,"title":2376,"slug":2377,"date":2378,"url":1288,"isVideo":1288,"description":2379,"tags":2380,"author":2382,"image":2383},"da7f5062-7c30-42e8-ab10-a5cb400cda12","Every Silent Hill Game, Ranked","every-silent-hill-game-ranked-worst-to-best","2024-10-04 15:40:00","(Updated September 2025) We rank every video game in Konami's Silent Hill franchise from worst to best by Metascore.",[2381],{"id":1780,"name":1781,"slug":1782},{"byline":1288,"firstName":2362,"id":2363,"lastName":2364,"username":2365},{"id":2384,"filename":2385,"dateCreated":2386,"alt":1288,"credits":2388,"path":2389,"cropGravity":1288,"crop":1288,"caption":2390,"typeName":1288,"imageUrl":1288,"width":1816,"height":1817,"sType":1288,"bucketType":1288,"bucketPath":1288,"mediaType":1288},"68798557-b481-4653-9506-cb11a232de0b","mainsilenthillgamesrankedrev.jpg",{"date":2387,"timezone":1794},"2025-09-22 17:54:42.000000","Konami / Metacritic","https://www.metacritic.com/a/img/2025/09/22/68798557-b481-4653-9506-cb11a232de0b/mainsilenthillgamesrankedrev.jpg","\u003Cp>When you hear the term \"survival horror\" in the video game  realm, \u003Cem>Resident Evil \u003C/em>and \u003Cem>Silent Hill \u003C/em>are likely the first two  franchises that come to mind. Throughout the years the Konami-developed \u003Cem>Silent Hill\u003C/em>  series, which started as atmospheric small-town mysteries that get  increasingly freaky  as you progress, has mutated outside of just games  with two movies (\u003Ca href=\"https://www.metacritic.com/movie/silent-hill/\">Silent Hill\u003C/a>, \u003Ca href=\"https://www.metacritic.com/movie/silent-hill-revelation-3d/\">Silent  Hill: Revelation\u003C/a>), books, pachinko machines, and even an appearance of the  dreaded Pyramid Head in the newly released \u003Ca href=\"https://www.metacritic.com/game/astro-bot/\">Astro Bot\u003C/a>. \u003C/p>\u003Cp>This month,  the franchise  is celebrating 25 years with a remake of one of the more  acclaimed titles in the series, \u003Cem>Silent Hill 2\u003C/em>. To celebrate that game's arrival, let's turn the  lights off and take a mysterious journey through the \u003Cem>Silent Hill\u003C/em>  video  game series as we rank each entry based on their Metascores,  representing the critical reaction to the games upon initial release   (with higher numbers on our 0-100 scale equating to better overall   reviews from top professional critics).&nbsp;\u003C/p>\u003Cp>Smartphone games, multi-game compilations, and repackages of existing  games (such as \"Director's Cut\" editions) have been excluded from the  list. And note that when a game has been released on multiple platforms,  we are only including the score for the platform that received the  largest quantity of reviews from professional critics. \u003C/p>",{"id":2392,"type":1820,"title":2393,"slug":2394,"date":2395,"url":1288,"isVideo":1288,"description":2396,"tags":2397,"author":2399,"image":2400},"9264e137-127f-41e1-a040-a7e59d58dfb1","The Best Video Games of 2024 So Far","best-video-games-of-2024-at-midyear","2024-06-27 15:47:00","We rank the highest-scoring new video games released during the first half of 2024.",[2398],{"id":1780,"name":1781,"slug":1782},{"byline":1784,"firstName":1785,"id":1786,"lastName":1787,"username":1788},{"id":2401,"filename":2402,"dateCreated":2403,"alt":1288,"credits":2405,"path":2406,"cropGravity":1288,"crop":1288,"caption":2407,"typeName":1288,"imageUrl":1288,"width":1816,"height":1817,"sType":1288,"bucketType":1288,"bucketPath":1288,"mediaType":1288},"8a6d4853-10d9-4cdb-abea-8893c6635d30","mainbestgames2024midyear.jpg",{"date":2404,"timezone":1794},"2024-06-27 15:47:21.000000","Square Enix / Metacritic","https://www.metacritic.com/a/img/2024/06/27/8a6d4853-10d9-4cdb-abea-8893c6635d30/mainbestgames2024midyear.jpg","\u003Cp>Which videogames  impressed critics  during the first half of the  year? On this page we rank the highest-scoring games with release dates  between January 1, 2024 and June 30, 2024. Titles are included based on  their Metascores as of June 26, 2024 and must have a \u003Cstrong>minimum of 7 reviews\u003C/strong> from professional critics to be eligible for inclusion.\u003C/p>\u003Cp>Note that ... \u003C/p>\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>If a game was released on multiple platforms, we included only the version receiving the largest total number of reviews\u003C/strong> (usually, but not always, the PS5 or PS4 version). \u003C/p>\u003Cp>\u003Cstrong>Multi-game compilations and newly released ports of  games released in recent years on other platforms are  excluded\u003C/strong>,  unless they are substantially different from the prior release(s) (for  example, an HD remaster  that also adds some new content or is multiple  hardware generations beyond the previous release). \u003Cstrong>Mobile games, \"Definitive\"/GOTY editions, and expansions/DLC are  also ineligible\u003C/strong>. (Yes, that means you won't find \u003Ca href=\"https://www.metacritic.com/game/elden-ring-shadow-of-the-erdtree/\">Shadow of the Erdtree\u003C/a> here.)\u003C/p>",{"id":2409,"type":1820,"title":2410,"slug":2411,"date":2412,"url":1288,"isVideo":1288,"description":2413,"tags":2414,"author":2416,"image":2417},"5049c2c8-77ee-42a8-b0b3-12ba41157406","Every Metacritic Game of the Year Winner","every-metacritic-game-of-the-year-winner","2024-06-11 00:00:00","(Updated January 2026) These are the best-reviewed games released each year in the 21st century.",[2415],{"id":1780,"name":1781,"slug":1782},{"byline":1784,"firstName":1785,"id":1786,"lastName":1787,"username":1788},{"id":2418,"filename":2419,"dateCreated":2420,"alt":1288,"credits":2422,"path":2423,"cropGravity":1288,"crop":1288,"caption":2424,"typeName":1288,"imageUrl":1288,"width":1816,"height":1817,"sType":1288,"bucketType":1288,"bucketPath":1288,"mediaType":1288},"2f578434-0805-461f-abbc-e65995e261dd","landinggameoftheyearwinners.jpg",{"date":2421,"timezone":1794},"2024-06-10 23:35:49.000000","Metacritic / Rockstar Games","https://www.metacritic.com/a/img/2024/06/10/2f578434-0805-461f-abbc-e65995e261dd/landinggameoftheyearwinners.jpg","\u003Cp>What were the best-reviewed games in every year in the 21st century?  Below are each of Metacritic's Game of the Year honorees for every year  since our launch in 2000, listed in reverse chronological order.\u003C/p>\u003Cp>What makes a game  a Metacritic Game of the Year recipient?  Basically, that title is given to the highest-scoring new game released  in each calendar year, with these qualifications:\u003C/p>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>The Game of the Year recipient has the highest Metascore (a number  from 0-100 representing the consensus opinion of top game review  publications), prior to rounding, for all games released in a calendar  year.\u003C/li>\u003Cli>Games \u003Cstrong>must have at least 7 reviews\u003C/strong> from professional critics to be eligible for inclusion\u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cstrong>For titles released  on multiple platforms, only the version receiving the largest total number of reviews is eligible\u003C/strong>.\u003C/li>\u003Cli>It must be a \"new\" game: If the same title was released the  previous year for other platforms, it does not qualify again in the  second year (each title can only be eligible in its first year).  However, remakes/remasters/ports are considered  \"new\" games if there  are significant changes in the new version. (There's no hard and fast  rule about what \"significant\" means here, but generally we're looking  for a decent amount of new playable content rather than mere cosmetic  upgrades.)\u003C/li>\u003Cli>Multi-game compilations, expansion packs/DLC, and Definitive/GOTY editions are  ineligible.\u003C/li>\u003Cli>Mobile games are also ineligible.\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"id":2426,"type":1773,"title":2427,"slug":2428,"date":2429,"url":1288,"isVideo":1288,"description":2430,"tags":2431,"author":2433,"image":2434},"444c919e-80a7-4e09-b126-265787c3061d","Metacritic's 14th Annual Game Publisher Rankings","2024-game-publisher-rankings","2024-03-21 13:00:00","We reveal the past year's best and worst video game publishers (based on their 2023 releases) in the 14th edition of our annual Game Publisher Rankings.",[2432],{"id":1780,"name":1781,"slug":1782},{"byline":1784,"firstName":1785,"id":1786,"lastName":1787,"username":1788},{"id":2435,"filename":2436,"dateCreated":2437,"alt":1288,"credits":1797,"path":2439,"cropGravity":1288,"crop":1288,"caption":1797,"typeName":1288,"imageUrl":1288,"width":1798,"height":1799,"sType":1288,"bucketType":1288,"bucketPath":1288,"mediaType":1288},"1e650cbb-7e95-4b1c-bc4c-ee1b379fb582","maingamepublishers2024.jpg",{"date":2438,"timezone":1794},"2024-03-20 23:36:10.000000","https://www.metacritic.com/a/img/2024/03/20/1e650cbb-7e95-4b1c-bc4c-ee1b379fb582/maingamepublishers2024.jpg",{"id":2441,"type":1820,"title":2442,"slug":2443,"date":2444,"url":1288,"isVideo":1288,"description":2445,"tags":2446,"author":2448,"image":2449},"e6f7765e-2bb5-44dd-b04c-e950c6718706","The 20 Best PC Games of 2023","best-pc-games-of-2023","2024-01-03 08:00:00","We rank the highest-scoring new PC games released in 2023.",[2447],{"id":1780,"name":1781,"slug":1782},{"byline":1784,"firstName":1785,"id":1786,"lastName":1787,"username":1788},{"id":2450,"filename":2451,"dateCreated":2452,"alt":1288,"credits":1288,"path":2454,"cropGravity":1288,"crop":1288,"caption":2455,"typeName":1288,"imageUrl":1288,"width":1798,"height":1799,"sType":1288,"bucketType":1288,"bucketPath":1288,"mediaType":1288},"d4fe29a3-1bc7-401f-ace1-f05498a990ab","games-yearend-pc-2023.jpg",{"date":2453,"timezone":1794},"2024-01-02 20:15:10.000000","https://www.metacritic.com/a/img/2024/01/02/d4fe29a3-1bc7-401f-ace1-f05498a990ab/games-yearend-pc-2023.jpg","\u003Cp>Which PC games  impressed professional reviewers the most during the  past year? This page  contains Metacritic's official list of the 20  best-reviewed titles released  between January 1, 2023 and December 31,  2023 ranked by Metascore. Games \u003Cstrong>must have at least 7 reviews\u003C/strong> from professional critics to be eligible for inclusion. \u003C/p>",{"id":2457,"type":1820,"titl