 their heels, the gang has to rob, steal and fight their way across the rugged heartland of America in order to survive. As deepening internal fissures threaten to tear the gang apart, Arthur must make a choice between his own ideals and loyalty to the gang that raised him. [Rockstar]",{"videoClosestPastAvailableDate":1288,"videoClosestFutureAvailableDate":1288,"videoClosestPastExpiryDate":1288,"videoClosestFutureExpiryDate":1288,"videoClosestPastAvailableNetworkId":1288,"videoClosestFutureAvailableNetworkId":1288,"videoClosestPastExpiryNetworkId":1288,"videoClosestFutureExpiryNetworkId":1288,"networkStreamingDates":1288},{"score":851},{"id":2742,"type":1649,"typeId":1650,"title":2743,"slug":2744,"premiereYear":2745,"releaseDate":2746,"rating":2684,"seoUrl":1288,"image":2747,"criticScoreSummary":2753,"genres":2755,"numberOfSeasons":15,"network":1288,"description":2757,"duration":15,"streamingDates":2758,"userScore":2759},1300110124,"Grand Theft Auto V","grand-theft-auto-v",2014,"2014-11-18",{"id":1288,"filename":2748,"dateCreated":2749,"alt":1288,"credits":1288,"path":1288,"cropGravity":1288,"crop":1288,"caption":1288,"typeName":1288,"imageUrl":1288,"width":2750,"height":2751,"sType":1288,"bucketType":1688,"bucketPath":2752,"mediaType":1288,"provider":1288},"6-1-675075-13.jpg",{"date":1288,"timezone":1288},795,1000,"/provider/6/3/6-1-675075-13.jpg",{"url":2754,"max":38,"score":2713,"reviewCount":24,"positiveCount":24,"neutralCount":15,"negativeCount":15,"sentiment":2671},"/game/grand-theft-auto-v/critic-reviews/",[2756],{"id":1288,"name":1712},"The sprawling sun-soaked metropolis of Los Santos is chock full of self-help coaches, starlets and C-List celebrities, once on top of the media world, now struggling to stay relevant in time of economic malaise and lowest-common-denominator reality TV. Amidst this madness, three unique criminals plan their own chances of survival and success: Franklin, a street-level hustler in search of opportunities for serious money; Micha