pling Hook and Deku Leaf to take the fight to spectacular, massive bosses. \n* Take on hordes of incredibly animated enemies as you search through riddle-filled dungeons.",{"videoClosestPastAvailableDate":1288,"videoClosestFutureAvailableDate":1288,"videoClosestPastExpiryDate":1288,"videoClosestFutureExpiryDate":1288,"videoClosestPastAvailableNetworkId":1288,"videoClosestFutureAvailableNetworkId":1288,"videoClosestPastExpiryNetworkId":1288,"videoClosestFutureExpiryNetworkId":1288,"networkStreamingDates":1288},{"score":851},{"id":2822,"type":1649,"typeId":1650,"title":2823,"slug":2824,"premiereYear":2825,"releaseDate":2826,"rating":2684,"seoUrl":1288,"image":2827,"criticScoreSummary":2831,"genres":2835,"numberOfSeasons":15,"network":1288,"description":2837,"duration":15,"streamingDates":2838,"userScore":2839},1300018488,"Grand Theft Auto: San Andreas","grand-theft-auto-san-andreas",2004,"2004-10-26",{"id":1288,"filename":2828,"dateCreated":2829,"alt":1288,"credits":1288,"path":1288,"cropGravity":1288,"crop":1288,"caption":1288,"typeName":1288,"imageUrl":1288,"width":1111,"height":2770,"sType":1288,"bucketType":1688,"bucketPath":2830,"mediaType":1288,"provider":1288},"6-1-53856-13.jpg",{"date":1288,"timezone":1288},"/provider/6/3/6-1-53856-13.jpg",{"url":2832,"max":38,"score":2833,"reviewCount":2815,"positiveCount":2834,"neutralCount":1120,"negativeCount":15,"sentiment":2671},"/game/grand-theft-auto-san-andreas/critic-reviews/",95,79,[2836],{"id":1288,"name":1712},"[Metacritic's 2004 PS2 Game of the Year]  Five years ago Carl Johnson escaped from the pressures of life in Los Santos, San Andreas... a city tearing itself apart with gang trouble, drugs and corruption. Where filmstars and millionaires do their best to avoid the dealers and gangbangers. Now, it's the early 90s. Carl's got to go home. His mother has been murdered, his family has fallen apart and his childhood friends are all heading towards disaster. On his return to the neighborhood, a couple of corrupt cops frame him for homicide. CJ is forced on a journey that takes him across the entire state of San Andreas, to save his family and to take control of the streets. [Rockstar]",{"videoClosestPastAvailableDate":1288,"videoClosestFutureAvailableDate":1288,"videoClosestPastExpiryDate":1288,"videoClosestFutureExpiryDate":1288,"videoClosestPastAvailableNetworkId":1288,"videoClosestFutureAvailableNetworkId":1288,"videoClosestPastExpiryNetworkId":1288,"videoClosestFutureExpiryNetworkId":1288,"networkStreamingDates":1288},{"score":2677},{"id":2841,"type":1649,"typeId":1650,"title":2842,"slug":2843,"premiereYear":2844,"releaseDate":2845,"rating":1713,"seoUrl":1288,"image":2846,"criticScoreSummary":2852,"genres":2855,"numberOfSeasons":15,"network":1288,"description":2857,"duration":15,"streamingDates":2858,"userScore":2859},1300679027,"The Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom - Nintendo Switch 2 Edition","the-legend-of-zelda-tears-of-the-kingdom-nintendo",2025,"2025-06-05",{"id":1288,"filename":2847,"dateCreated":2848,"alt":1288,"credits":1288,"path":1288,"cropGravity":1288,"crop":1288,"caption":1288,"typeName":1288,"imageUrl":1288,"width":2849,"height":2850,"sType":1288,"bucketType":1688,"bucketPath":2851,"mediaType":1288,"provider":1288},"7-1749776519.jpg",{"date":1288,"timezone":1288},426,617,"/provider/7/2/7-1749776519.jpg",{"url":2853,"max":38,"score":2833,"reviewCount":2854,"positiveCount":2854,"neutralCount":15,"negativeCount":15,"sentiment":2671},"/game/the-legend-of-zelda-tears-of-the-kingdom-nintendo/critic-reviews/",18,[2856],{"id":1288,"name":1712},"Upgrade your adventures in Hyrule on the Nintendo Switch 2 system! Jump back into the Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild and The Legend of Zelda: Tears of the Kingdom games, now with enhanced resolution, increased frame rates, HDR support, and faster load times.\r\n\r\nPlus, you can get even more out of your adventures with ZELDA NOTES. Use Navigation to find shrines and Koroks, hear previously untold stories from in-game characters, share Autobuild blueprints, and more! This game-specific service is designed to provide a more streamlined gameplay experience.",{"videoClosestPastAvailableDate":1288,"videoClosestFutureAvailableDate":1288,"videoClosestPastExpiryDate":1288,"videoClosestFutureExpiryDate":1288,"videoClosestPastAvailableNetworkId":1288,"videoClosestFutureAvailableNetworkId":1288,"videoClosestPastExpiryNetworkId":1288,"videoClosestFutureExpiryNetworkId":1288,"networkStreamingDates":1288},{"score":2760},{"id":2861,"type":1649,"typeId":1650,"title":2862,"slug":2863,"premiereYear":2864,"releaseDate":2865,"rating":2684,"seoUrl":1288,"image":2866,"criticScoreSummary":2870,"genres":2873,"numberOfSeasons":15,"network":1288,"description":2875,"duration":15,"streamingDates":2876,"userScore":2877},1300004716,"Grand Theft Auto: Vice City","grand-theft-auto-vice-city",2002,"2002-10-29",{"id":1288,"filename":2867,"dateCreated":2868,"alt":1288,"credits":1288,"path":1288,"cropGravity":1288,"crop":1288,"caption":1288,"typeName":1288,"imageUrl":1288,"width":1111,"height":2770,"sType":1288,"bucketType":1688,"bucketPath":2869,"mediaType":1288,"provider":1288},"6-1-18290-13.jpg",{"date":1288,"timezone":1288},"/provider/6/3/6-1-18290-13.jpg",{"url":2871,"max":38,"score":2833,"reviewCount":2872,"positiveCount":2872,"neutralCount":15,"negativeCount":15,"sentiment":2671},"/game/grand-theft-auto-vice-city/critic-reviews/",62,[2874],{"id":1288,"name":1712},"[Metacritic's 2002 PS2 Game of the Year ] Welcome to Vice City. Welcome to the 1980s. Having just made it back onto the streets of Liberty City after a long stretch in maximum security, Tommy Vercetti is sent to Vice City by his old boss, Sonny Forelli. They were understandably nervous about his re-appearance in Liberty City, so a trip down south seemed like a good idea. But all does not go smoothly upon his arrival in the glamorous, hedonistic metropolis of Vice City. He's set up and is left with no money and no merchandise. Sonny wants his money back, but the biker gangs, Cuban gangsters, and corrupt politicians stand in his way. Most of Vice City seems to want Tommy dead. His only answer is to fight back and take over the city himself. Vice City offers vehicular pleasures to suit every taste. For the speed enthusiast, there's high-performance cars and motorbikes. For the sportsman, a powerboat or a golf buggy lets you enjoy the great outdoors. For those that need that sense of freedom and escape, why not charter a helicopter and see the beauty of Vice City from the air? [Rockstar]",{"videoClosestPastAvailableDate":1288,"videoClosestFutureAvailableDate":1288,"videoClosestPastExpiryDate":1288,"videoClosestFutureExpiryDate":1288,"videoClosestPastAvailableNetworkId":1288,"videoClosestFutureAvailableNetworkId":1288,"videoClosestPastExpiryNetworkId":1288,"videoClosestFutureExpiryNetworkId":1288,"networkStreamingDates":1288},{"score":2878},8.6,{"id":2880,"type":1649,"typeId":1650,"title":2881,"slug":2882,"premiereYear":2864,"releaseDate":2883,"rating":2661,"seoUrl":1288,"image":2884,"criticScoreSummary":2888,"genres":2891,"numberOfSeasons":15,"network":1288,"description":2893,"duration":15,"streamingDates":2894,"userScore":2895},1300563786,"The Legend of Zelda: A Link to the Past / Four Swords","the-legend-of-zelda-a-link-to-the-past-four-swords","2002-12-03",{"id":1288,"filename":2885,"dateCreated":2886,"alt":1288,"credits":1288,"path":1288,"cropGravity":1288,"crop":1288,"caption":1288,"typeName":1288,"imageUrl":1288,"width":1111,"height":1111,"sType":1288,"bucketType":1688,"bucketPath":2887,"mediaType":1288,"provider":1288},"6-1-18316-13.jpg",{"date":1288,"timezone":1288},"/provider/6/3/6-1-18316-13.jpg",{"url":2889,"max":38,"score":2833,"reviewCount":1128,"positiveCount":2890,"neutralCount":1120,"negativeCount":15,"sentiment":2671},"/game/the-legend-of-zelda-a-link-to-the-past-four-swords/critic-reviews/",29,[2892],{"id":1288,"name":1712},"Now you have a link to one of the greatest adventures in The Legend of Zelda series.  The Legend of Zelda: A Link to the Past revives the classic SNES game on the Game Boy Advance and adds a new multiplayer mode.  In a Link to the Past, Link travels between the light world and the dark world, conquering fierce monsters and uncovering Hyrule's deepest secrets along the way.  Also included is Four Swords, which lets you play with up to three other players, slashing through dungeons and collecting rupees.  Whether you choose solo or competitive play, The Legend of Zelda will keep you occupied with its brain-bending puzzles and fun swashbuckling action.",{"videoClosestPastAvailableDate":1288,"videoClosestFutureAvailableDate":1288,"videoClosestPastExpiryDate":1288,"videoClosestFutureExpiryDate":1288,"videoClosestPastAvailableNetworkId":1288,"videoClosestFutureAvailableNetworkId":1288,"videoClosestPastExpiryNetworkId":1288,"videoClosestFutureExpiryNetworkId":1288,"networkStreamingDates":1288},{"score":2801},{"id":2897,"type":1649,"typeId":1650,"title":2898,"slug":2899,"premiereYear":2900,"releaseDate":2901,"rating":2661,"seoUrl":1288,"image":2902,"criticScoreSummary":2907,"genres":2910,"numberOfSeasons":15,"network":1288,"description":2912,"duration":15,"streamingDates":2913,"userScore":2914},1300001289,"The Legend of Zelda: Majora's Mask","the-legend-of-zelda-majoras-mask",2000,"2000-10-25",{"id":1288,"filename":2903,"dateCreated":2904,"alt":1288,"credits":1288,"path":1288,"cropGravity":1288,"crop":1288,"caption":1288,"typeName":1288,"imageUrl":1288,"width":1111,"height":2905,"sType":1288,"bucketType":1688,"bucketPath":2906,"mediaType":1288,"provider":1288},"6-1-4758-13.jpg",{"date":1288,"timezone":1288},901,"/provider/6/3/6-1-4758-13.jpg",{"url":2908,"max":38,"score":2833,"reviewCount":2909,"positiveCount":2909,"neutralCount":15,"negativeCount":15,"sentiment":2671},"/game/the-legend-of-zelda-majoras-mask/critic-reviews/",27,[2911],{"id":1288,"name":1712},"Thrown into a parallel world by the mischievous actions of a possessed Skull Kid