uilt from the ground up to create the most dynamic and vivid vision of Zelda’s kingdom yet. This is Hyrule as you’ve always imagined it. Playing the Ocarina Link needs to play the eponymous Ocarina of Time many, many times over the course of the game. This involves a specific series of button presses to play one of the twelve songs in the game. In the original title, you would need to assign the ocarina to an item slot, then likely review the button prompts to your song, then play them from memory. The Nintendo 3DS version has the ocarina constantly available on the Touch Screen, and playing with the button prompts for each song right in front of you. Enhanced Game play While the greatest care has been taken to preserve the classic game play and story, a number of new features make this the definitive version of this extraordinary game.",{"videoClosestPastAvailableDate":1288,"videoClosestFutureAvailableDate":1288,"videoClosestPastExpiryDate":1288,"videoClosestFutureExpiryDate":1288,"videoClosestPastAvailableNetworkId":1288,"videoClosestFutureAvailableNetworkId":1288,"videoClosestPastExpiryNetworkId":1288,"videoClosestFutureExpiryNetworkId":1288,"networkStreamingDates":1288},{"score":2677},{"id":3010,"type":1649,"typeId":1650,"title":3011,"slug":3012,"premiereYear":3013,"releaseDate":3014,"rating":2684,"seoUrl":1288,"image":3015,"criticScoreSummary":3020,"genres":3023,"numberOfSeasons":15,"network":1288,"description":3025,"duration":15,"streamingDates":3026,"userScore":3027},1300038520,"Grand Theft Auto: Chinatown Wars","grand-theft-auto-chinatown-wars",2009,"2009-03-17",{"id":1288,"filename":3016,"dateCreated":3017,"alt":1288,"credits":1288,"path":1288,"cropGravity":1288,"crop":1288,"caption":1288,"typeName":1288,"imageUrl":1288,"width":1111,"height":3018,"sType":1288,"bucketType":1688,"bucketPath":3019,"mediaType":1288,"provider":1288},"6-1-101495-13.jpg",{"date":1288,"timezone":1288},570,"/provider/6/3/6-1-101495-13.jpg",{"url":3021,"max":38,"score":3022,"reviewCo