ughing at a perfectly timed gag, the game delivers a rich, polished experience that honors the Dark Knight in a way only LEGO can.","https://www.impulsegamer.com/lego-batman-legacy-of-the-dark-knight-review-ps5-playstation-5/","2026-05-18","Impulsegamer","impulsegamer",{"id":1733,"type":2578,"title":1651,"url":1362,"criticScoreSummary":3383,"platform":3384,"gameTaxonomy":3385},{"url":1732,"score":1658},{"id":3264,"name":1655},{"game":3386,"platform":3387},{"id":1733,"name":1651},{"id":3264,"name":1655},{"quote":3389,"score":22,"url":3390,"date":3379,"author":1797,"authorSlug":1288,"image":1288,"publicationName":3391,"publicationSlug":3392,"reviewedProduct":3393,"platform":1655},"Appearances can be deceiving - especially when it comes to grown adults willingly sinking hours into this phenomenal LEGO game. This is easily one of the best, if not the best, pieces of Batman fan service ever made, and a must-play for anyone who grew up with the films, games, and animated series. It also stands as the most ambitious, and arguably the best, LEGO game ever created.","https://adria.ign.com/lego-batman-legacy-of-the-dark-knight/51944/lego-batman-legacy-of-the-dark-knight-recenzija","IGN Adria","ign-adria",{"id":1733,"type":2578,"title":1651,"url":1362,"criticScoreSummary":3394,"platform":3395,"gameTaxonomy":3396},{"url":1732,"score":1658},{"id":3264,"name":1655},{"game":3397,"platform":3398},{"id":1733,"name":1651},{"id":3264,"name":1655},{"quote":3400,"score":3003,"url":3401,"date":3379,"author":1797,"authorSlug":1288,"image":1288,"publicationName":3402,"publicationSlug":3403,"reviewedProduct":3404,"platform":1655},"LEGO Batman: The Dark Knight's Legacy clearly stands out as a game crafted with immense affection and respect for the DC Comics license. Its open-world recreation of Gotham City is an absolute stroke of genius, and the sheer level of detail it contains is sure to astonish fans of the Caped Crusader. Furthermore, the developers have seized the opportunity to pack the game with a wealth of content—much of which proves highly inspired—contributing to truly exceptional replayability.","https://vandal.elespanol.com/analisis/ps5/lego-batman-legacy-of-the-dark-knight/214407#p-89","Vandal","vandal",{"id":1733,"type":2578,"title":1651,"url":1362,"criticScoreSummary":3405,"platform":3406,"gameTaxonomy":3407},{"url":1732,"score":1658},{"id":3264,"name":1655},{"game":3408,"platform":3409},{"id":1733,"name":1651},{"id":3264,"name":1655},{"quote":3411,"score":3003,"url":3412,"date":3379,"author":1797,"authorSlug":1288,"image":1288,"publicationName":3413,"publicationSlug":3414,"reviewedProduct":3415,"platform":1655},"Lego Batman: Legacy of the Dark Knight is a highly entertaining title that successfully combines the charm expected from Lego games with gameplay reminiscent of the Arkham series, delivering a great tribute to the Dark Knight that can provide hours of fun. However, frequent graphical issues keep it from reaching perfection.","https://tierragamer.com/resenas/videojuegos/lego-batman-legacy-of-the-dark-knight-es-un-arkham-light-con-mucho-potencial-para-la-diversion","TierraGamer","tierragamer",{"id":1733,"type":2578,"title":1651,"url":1362,"criticScoreSummary":3416,"platform":3417,"gameTaxonomy":3418},{"url":1732,"score":1658},{"id":3264,"name":1655},{"game":3419,"platform":3420},{"id":1733,"name":1651},{"id":3264,"name":1655},{"quote":3422,"score":2815,"url":3423,"date":3379,"author":1797,"authorSlug":1288,"image":1288,"publicationName":3424,"publicationSlug":3425,"reviewedProduct":3426,"platform":1655},"Legacy of the Dark Knight isn’t just one of the best LEGO Batman games—it’s one of the best Batman games and one of the best LEGO games, an experience that delivers on virtually every level. It’s even better when played in co-op.","https://www.eurogamer.pt/lego-batman-legcy-of-the-dark-knight-review-um-dos-melhores-jogos-batman","Eurogamer Portugal","eurogamer-portugal",{"id":1733,"type":2578,"title":1651,"url":1362,"criticScoreSummary":3427,"platform":3428,"gameTaxonomy":3429},{"url":1732,"score":1658},{"id":3264,"name":1655},{"game":3430,"platform":3431},{"id":1733,"name":1651},{"id":3264,"name":1655},{"quote":3433,"score":2815,"url":3434,"date":3379,"author":1797,"authorSlug":1288,"image":1288,"publicationName":3435,"publicationSlug":3436,"reviewedProduct":3437,"platform":1655},"The closest thing to a new Batman: Arkham game there’ll be for many years and a great co-op adventure in its own right, that somehow manages to be unpredictable all the way through.","https://metro.co.uk/2026/05/18/lego-batman-legacy-dark-knight-review-arkham-co-op-nights-28416855/","Metro GameCentral","metro-gamecentral",{"id":1733,"type":2578,"title":1651,"url":1362,"criticScoreSummary":3438,"platform":3439,"gameTaxonomy":3440},{"url":1732,"score":1658},{"id":3264,"name":1655},{"game":3441,"platform":3442},{"id":1733,"name":1651},{"id":3264,"name":1655},{"quote":3444,"score":3445,"url":3446,"date":3379,"author":1797,"authorSlug":1288,"image":1288,"publicationName":3447,"publicationSlug":3448,"reviewedProduct":3449,"platform":1655},"LEGO Batman: Legacy of the Dark Knight is a pretty entertaining and comedic experience for all fans of Batman especially when it has many deep references to the movies, comic lore and TV series. However, it lacks innovation because the LEGO game series still follows the same comfort zone formula with its repetitive activities.",70,"https://www.true-gaming.net/home/632435/legobatman-lotdk","TrueGaming","truegaming",{"id":1733,"type":2578,"title":1651,"url":1362,"criticScoreSummary":3450,"platform":3451,"gameTaxonomy":3452},{"url":1732,"score":1658},{"id":3264,"name":1655},{"game":3453,"platform":3454},{"id":1733,"name":1651},{"id":3264,"name":1655},[3456,3463,3474,3485,3496,3507,3518],{"quote":3377,"score":38,"url":3378,"date":3379,"author":1797,"authorSlug":1288,"image":1288,"publicationName":3380,"publicationSlug":3381,"reviewedProduct":3457,"platform":1655},{"id":1733,"type":2578,"title":1651,"url":1362,"criticScoreSummary":3458,"platform":3459,"gameTaxonomy":3460},{"url":1732,"score":1658},{"id":3264,"name":1655},{"game":3461,"platform":3462},{"id":1733,"name":1651},{"id":3264,"name":1655},{"quote":3464,"score":38,"url":3465,"date":3379,"author":1797,"authorSlug":1288,"image":1288,"publicationName":3466,"publicationSlug":3467,"reviewedProduct":3468,"platform":1655},"The end result is a fun, funny, and self-aware homage to the Dark Knight that is equal parts LEGO wackiness and phenomenal Batman Arkham successor. LEGO Batman: Legacy of the Dark Knight is one of the best LEGO games of all time. Heck, it might just be THE best LEGO game ever. And it'll certainly give your favorite Arkham game a run for its money.","https://screenrant.com/lego-batman-legacy-of-the-dark-knight-review/","Screen Rant","screen-rant",{"id":1733,"type":2578,"title":1651,"url":1362,"criticScoreSummary":3469,"platform":3470,"gameTaxonomy":3471},{"url":1732,"score":1658},{"id":3264,"name":1655},{"game":3472,"platform":3473},{"id":1733,"name":1651},{"id":3264,"name":1655},{"quote":3475,"score":38,"url":3476,"date":3379,"author":1797,"authorSlug":1288,"image":1288,"publicationName":3477,"publicationSlug":3478,"reviewedProduct":3479,"platform":1655},"LEGO Batman: Legacy of the Dark Knight is impossible to put down. It manages to imbue the intensity of Gotham with just the right level of whimsy and humour. The game’s perfectly crafted open-world and varied mission design don’t simply just make it a blast to play; it also makes the game very good value for money, and that goes a long way these days. LEGO Batman: Legacy of the Dark Knight deserves to stand proud as one of the best games of 2026 and within LEGO and Batman’s history.","https://www.gamingbible.com/reviews/lego-batman-legacy-of-the-dark-knight-review-350548-20260518","GAMINGbible","gamingbible",{"id":1733,"type":2578,"title":1651,"url":1362,"criticScoreSummary":3480,"platform":3481,"gameTaxonomy":3482},{"url":1732,"score":1658},{"id":3264,"name":1655},{"game":3483,"platform":3484},{"id":1733,"name":1651},{"id":3264,"name":1655},{"quote":3486,"score":38,"url":3487,"date":3379,"author":1797,"authorSlug":1288,"image":1288,"publicationName":3488,"publicationSlug":3489,"reviewedProduct":3490,"platform":1655},"LEGO Batman: Legacy of the Dark Knight is the best love letter to Batman we’ve ever seen. The way it handles the history of the World's Greatest Detective is incredible. With great combat mechanics, a fun and fantastical story that gives the cornerstone eras their turn, this is, hands down, the best LEGO game to date.","https://www.cgmagonline.com/review/game/lego-batman-legacy-of-the-dark-knight/","CGMagazine","cgmagazine",{"id":1733,"type":2578,"title":1651,"url":1362,"criticScoreSummary":3491,"platform":3492,"gameTaxonomy":3493},{"url":1732,"score":1658},{"id":3264,"name":1655},{"game":3494,"platform":3495},{"id":1733,"name":1651},{"id":3264,"name":1655},{"quote":3497,"score":2833,"url":3498,"date":3379,"author":1797,"authorSlug":1288,"image":1288,"publicationName":3499,"publicationSlug":3500,"reviewedProduct":3501,"platform":1655},"LEGO Batman: The Dark Knight’s Legacy manages to go beyond the classic formula of other games in the franchise, offering a fully immersive experience in the complex city of Gotham and unraveling Batman’s legacy through an original, epic, and entertaining story. It is a “love letter” to fans of the Caped Crusader and a tribute to the Dark Knight’s legacy.","https://br.ign.com/lego-batman-legacy-of-the-dark-knight/153057/lego-batman-legacy-of-the-dark-knight-ultrapassa-classica-formula-e-traz-imersao-completa-ao-univers","IGN Brasil","ign-brasil",{"id":1733,"type":2578,"title":1651,"url":1362,"criticScoreSummary":3502,"platform":3503,"gameTaxonomy":3504},{"url":1732,"score":1658},{"id":3264,"name":1655},{"game":3505,"platform":3506},{"id":1733,"name":1651},{"id":3264,"name":1655},{"quote":3508,"score":22,"url":3509,"date":3379,"author":1797,"authorSlug":1288,"image":1288,"publicationName":3510,"publicationSlug":3511,"reviewedProduct":3512,"platform":1655},"As we wait for the Dark Knight's next big game, LEGO Batman: Legacy of the Dark Knight steps in and delivers a lovingly crafted, satisfying entry. It pulls from the best Batman entries while going beyond expectations in every aspect. This one’s by the fans, for the fans.","https://gamingbolt.com/lego-batman-legacy-of-the-dark-knight-review-lets-put-a-smile-on-that-face","GamingBolt","gamingbolt",{"id":1733,"type":2578,"title":1651,"url":1362,"criticScoreSummary":3513,"platform":3514,"gameTaxonomy":3515},{"url":1732,"score":1658},{"id":3264,"name":1655},{"game":3516,"platform":3517},{"id":1733,"name":1651},{"id":3264,"name":1655},{"quote":3519,"score":22,"url":3520,"date":3379,"author":1797,"authorSlug":1288,"image":1288,"publicationName":3521,"publicationSlug":3522,"reviewedProduct":3523,"platform":1655},"Whether as a first Batman game or a revisit of franchise lore, Legacy of the Dark Knight presents a rich adventure of layered twists, complete with solid and approachable gameplay, along with that well-balanced, laugh-out-loud humour. As an ode to such a prolific franchise, there’s so much the game gets right.","https://www.screenhub.com.au/news/reviews/lego-batman-legacy-of-the-dark-knight-review-2699976/","ScreenHub","screenhub",{"id":1733,"type":2578,"title":1651,"url":1362,"criticScoreSummary":3524,"platform":3525,"gameTaxonomy":3526},{"url":1732,"score":1658},{"id":3264,"name":1655},{"game":3527,"platform":3528},{"id":1733,"name":1651},{"id":3264,"name":1655},[],[3531,3542,3553,3564,3575],{"quote":3532,"score":3445,"url":3533,"date":3379,"author":1797,"authorSlug":1288,"image":1288,"publicationName":3534,"publicationSlug":3535,"reviewedProduct":3536,"platform":1655},"Filled to the brim with content that will excite every Batman fan, Legacy of the Dark Knight ist yet another fun Lego romp that slightly misses the mark by relying too much on boring combat sections.","https://de.ign.com/lego-batman-legacy-of-the-dark-knight/152627/lego-batman-im-test-das-vermachtnis-des-dunklen-ritters-mehr-fanservice-geht-nicht","IGN Deutschland","ign-deutschland",{"id":1733,"type":2578,"title":1651,"url":1362,"criticScoreSummary":3537,"platform":3538,"gameTaxonomy":3539},{"url":1732,"score":1658},{"id":3264,"name":1655},{"game":3540,"platform":3541},{"id":1733,"name":1651},{"id":3264,"name":1655},{"quote":3543,"score":3445,"url":3544,"date":3379,"author":1797,"authorSlug":1288,"image":1288,"publicationName":3545,"publicationSlug":3546,"reviewedProduct":3547,"platform":1655},"LEGO Batman: The Dark Knight Legacy is a safe bet—perhaps even too safe. It checks all the expected boxes without ever taking any risks. Worse still, it tries to have it both ways without ever fully satisfying players on either front. Fans will undoubtedly find something to enjoy, thanks in particular to the richness of the universe and the numerous references. But those hoping for a more significant evolution of the formula may be left wanting. This new installment of LEGO Batman thus fulfills its purpose with diligence. Accessible, generous, and faithful to the spirit of the franchise, it offers a pleasant and familiar adventure—for better or for worse... Another brick in a solid edifice, but one that could certainly use a bit of a refresh.","https://fr.ign.com/lego-batman-legacy-of-the-dark-knight/88558/test-lego-batman-lheritage-du-chevalier-noir-une-brique-de-plus-dans-la-legende","IGN France","ign-france",{"id":1733,"type":2578,"title":1651,"url":1362,"criticScoreSummary":3548,"platform":3549,"gameTaxonomy":3550},{"url":1732,"score":1658},{"id":3264,"name":1655},{"game":3551,"platform":3552},{"id":1733,"name":1651},{"id":3264,"name":1655},{"quote":3554,"score":3445,"url":3555,"date":3379,"author":1797,"authorSlug":1288,"image":1288,"publicationName":3556,"publicationSlug":3557,"reviewedProduct":3558,"platform":1655},"This LEGO Batman : Legacy of the Dark Knight is a true love letter to DC’s massive franchise. If you’re a fan of the Caped Crusader, you’ll be delighted to find all these iconic references that have endured through the decades. And if you’re less of a Batman fan, then this LEGO game is a great way to discover Bruce Wayne’s story, LEGO-style, while having a great time...Unlike the older LEGO Batman titles, this one offers a larger world, a wider variety of enemies and bosses, even if the combat can sometimes feel repetitive, and above all, a story that almost completely retells everything from A to Z. In short, it’s a really enjoyable game to play, with, of course, plenty of side quests and collectibles to hunt down, just like any good LEGO-branded game.","https://www.gamekult.com/jeux/lego-batman-legacy-of-the-dark-knight-3050888741/test.html","Gamekult","gamekult",{"id":1733,"type":2578,"title":1651,"url":1362,"criticScoreSummary":3559,"platform":3560,"gameTaxonomy":3561},{"url":1732,"score":1658},{"id":3264,"name":1655},{"game":3562,"platform":3563},{"id":1733,"name":1651},{"id":3264,"name":1655},{"quote":3565,"score":3445,"url":3566,"date":3379,"author":1797,"authorSlug":1288,"image":1288,"publicationName":3567,"publicationSlug":3568,"reviewedProduct":3569,"platform":1655},"Legacy of the Dark Knight tries to honour many legacies at once, and struggles to serve them all effectively. A familiar but fun LEGO game, a functional and simplified continuation of the Batman: Arkham series’ mechanics and an unambitious and only intermittently funny Batman story all sit alongside one another in a final build of a game that will still be enjoyed by many, but is never quite the sum of its bricks and will unlikely have much of a legacy of its own.","https://checkpointgaming.net/reviews/2026/05/lego-batman-legacy-of-the-dark-knight-review-brick-ham-city/","Checkpoint Gaming","checkpoint-gaming",{"id":1733,"type":2578,"title":1651,"url":1362,"criticScoreSummary":3570,"platform":3571,"gameTaxonomy":3572},{"url":